title: [LucarioPK Subs] Detective Conan SP 712-715 - Hattori Heiji and
description:
The very very spooky vampire-filled super-charged special is now here. I've compiled the entire month's worth of episodes into a tidy package. Get comfy and watch, this is 84 minutes of pure mystery!

You are free to do whatever you like with this file, and upload it wherever you want, etc! Just make sure you give credit to Kitsunekko as well as myself. :) Oh and please make sure the website doesn't have questionable content on it, I'd like to remain as family-friendly as possible!

I'll be back Thursday with Pokemon XY 04, and next Saturday with Conan 716!
